Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.77,0:00:05.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.56,0:00:13.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.49,0:00:33.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.46,0:00:36.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sound resonates\NInto my heart, so hard and deep
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:40.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A field of stars spans endlessly\NAnd through it I carve a passageway
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.32,0:00:42.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In step with time as generations change
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.19,0:00:44.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Close your eyes and listen closely
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.19,0:00:47.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shooting stars stream on silently…\Nuntil the goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.19,0:00:50.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep the light inside of you,\Nnever give up don't ever lose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:52.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Transcend time and you will prove,\Nthere is a special place for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.09,0:00:53.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A blaze of glory is there,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.93,0:00:56.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all a part of our estate;\Nlife is our story to create
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.97,0:01:01.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.64,0:01:05.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old by voice of light\NThroughout the age, never fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.54,0:01:09.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A secret fire, a scream of light,\Nvoices calling through twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:11.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cast your thoughts to the wind,\Nhang your wishes on the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.22,0:01:13.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Live your life with all your strength\Nfor dreams will reach you very soon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.44,0:01:16.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.10,0:01:19.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old\Nby voice of light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.07,0:01:21.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Throughout the age,\Nnever fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.16,0:01:24.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Someday your dream will find\Nits place somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.05,0:01:28.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep shining like a star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.16,0:01:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.78,0:01:49.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right, explain to me...\Nthe rules of this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.20,0:01:55.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.19,0:02:00.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.32,0:02:03.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s bait for Hollows.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.19,0:02:06.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I crush it and scatter it around,\NHollows will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.40,0:02:08.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.74,0:02:11.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The victor will be whoever kills
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.37,0:02:14.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the most Hollows that\Ngather in 24 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.19,0:02:18.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Isn’t that easy to understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.65,0:02:20.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Quit kidding around!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.97,0:02:22.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’d endanger the lives of\Nthe town’s people
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.25,0:02:24.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,just for our battle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.19,0:02:26.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just who do you think you are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.19,0:02:29.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t make such a fuss, braggart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.11,0:02:32.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No need to worry about other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.95,0:02:36.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll kill every single\NHollow that comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.19,0:02:43.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you are confident that\Nyou can protect others from Hollows,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.15,0:02:46.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,then you should accept\Nthis challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.57,0:03:24.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.28,0:03:35.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of face is that,\NIchigo Kurosaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.49,0:03:37.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Change it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:39.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chase away the Hollows!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:44.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Soon, the town will be overflowing\Nwith Hollows lured here by the bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:46.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s just say the die is cast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.21,0:03:47.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.53,0:03:50.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t there something else\Nyou should be doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.82,0:03:52.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,besides grabbing onto me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.82,0:04:00.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s if you really want\Nto protect
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.75,0:04:03.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,as many people as possible\Nfrom the Hollows...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:09.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why you--!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.19,0:04:11.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.49,0:04:17.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hollows tend to attack those\Nwith high spiritual energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.65,0:04:27.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzu! Karin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.25,0:04:28.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.15,0:04:30.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.24,0:04:35.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn’t noticed, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.32,0:04:38.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That there are people\Naround him
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.57,0:04:41.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,with high spiritual powers\Nbesides his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.07,0:04:44.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But don’t worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:46.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll kill every one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.61,0:04:52.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And...you’ll realize how\Nweak your own power is,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.82,0:04:55.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,here at the point of no return.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:13.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I detest Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.03,0:05:22.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s true.\NYou’re the cutest of all, Mika!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.33,0:05:24.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Truly?\NCan I really believe you, Yoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.50,0:05:26.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.40,0:05:27.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How's about a hug?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.74,0:05:30.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Someone will see us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.20,0:05:35.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!\NQuit making out in broad daylight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:37.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re just ghosts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.03,0:05:40.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s all right. No one is looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:42.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mika!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.21,0:05:43.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:48.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Arisawa! Break’s over!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:51.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Arisawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.32,0:05:53.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.20,0:05:58.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:01.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Orihime?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.11,0:06:04.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:10.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right...that day when\NI went to Orihime’s house...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:14.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have almost no recollection\Nof that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.90,0:06:19.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just that I felt so much pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.03,0:06:26.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and that I thought I saw\Nsomeone who looked like Rukia...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.19,0:06:32.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At first, I thought I was dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:35.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But when I mentioned it to\NOrihime the following day
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.82,0:06:38.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,she had seen the very same dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.19,0:06:41.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And ever since that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.82,0:06:44.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I started to see strange things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.86,0:06:49.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:53.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– I can see you!\N– Hey Tatsuki...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.74,0:06:59.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You and I are butt friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.38,0:07:01.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Aghh! It’s so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:03.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:06.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I’m sorry. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:11.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... it’s not that important, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:14.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what’s going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.92,0:07:16.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The windows on the first floor\Nare shattered!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.67,0:07:18.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Anyone hurt?!\N– I wonder what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.57,0:07:19.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go, Orihime.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.03,0:07:20.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:33.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.57,0:07:40.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Kurosaki!\NHurry and kick it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.70,0:08:10.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Number three!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.19,0:08:13.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.28,0:08:17.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She’s probably gone somewhere\Nto play around this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.03,0:08:21.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where could she be?! Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.86,0:08:25.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.49,0:08:27.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:29.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:35.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:42.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Eleven.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.15,0:08:54.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Urahara?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.57,0:08:56.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.11,0:08:58.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A Hollow...\Nat a time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.95,0:09:01.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry Urahara,\Nwe’ll continue this later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.62,0:09:07.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What? The signal is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.49,0:09:17.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I get it. Ichigo is doing pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:26.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Gone again?\NWhat’s happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:29.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not really broken, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:31.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.78,0:09:35.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So many Hollows,\Nat this rate is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.19,0:09:39.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,not...possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.03,0:10:02.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What does this heavy and\Nagitated Sprit Energy mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.32,0:10:10.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just what is happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:39.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:10:56.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.19,0:11:16.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry it up, Chad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:20.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep stalling,\Nlunch specials will be over!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:22.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll make you pay the difference!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.56,0:11:24.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That won’t do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.61,0:11:28.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn right that won’t do!\NSo move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.61,0:11:36.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What a bad feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.74,0:11:39.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve had this feeling before...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.49,0:11:46.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.23,0:11:48.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out, will you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.19,0:11:50.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m eking out a living with\Nwhat I make from my part-time job!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.58,0:11:52.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My life’s as tenuous as a bug’s!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.37,0:11:56.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not like you carefree students\Nwho can eat just by being alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:11:57.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.19,0:12:00.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I risk my life just for\Na bowl of rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.16,0:12:01.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Repeat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:03.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-I risk my life just for\Na bowl of rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.54,0:12:05.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right. If you get it,\Nlet’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.37,0:12:08.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Unless it’s on sale,\Ndon’t buy meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:10.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The expiration date is\Njust an approximation! Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.11,0:12:14.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What’s happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.99,0:12:17.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Was that a gas explosion?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.86,0:12:21.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:24.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just that area is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:27.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Chad! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.19,0:12:30.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:38.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shigeo! Harutoki! Run--!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.19,0:12:48.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He’s coming after me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:53.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.95,0:12:57.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad! Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.19,0:13:03.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know what that\Nbig thing is,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.74,0:13:06.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but if it’s targeting me,\Nthen it’s simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.00,0:13:08.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I just have to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.49,0:13:11.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Run to where there’s\Nno one around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:13.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.20,0:13:17.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oops, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:22.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki! What’s with you anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.16,0:13:24.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You space out then kick\Nthe ball just anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:26.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious about playing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.03,0:13:27.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.19,0:13:31.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What, y-you wanna fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.19,0:13:33.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.15,0:13:35.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll show you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.53,0:13:38.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry. I think I’ll go home,\Nafter all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.19,0:13:40.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.19,0:13:44.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Wait, Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.53,0:13:47.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s no good today...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:50.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I keep thinking about\Nthat weird air
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:52.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and can’t concentrate on soccer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.57,0:13:54.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll take a bath and go to bed early.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.19,0:14:08.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re Ichigo’s friend.\NThe one with the parakeet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.65,0:14:12.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo’s sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.19,0:14:15.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What’s a grown up like\Nyou doing here alone--?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:28.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.49,0:14:32.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.49,0:14:33.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:45.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It stopped moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.19,0:14:49.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is it watching our moves? Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.32,0:14:54.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:56.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I could see him\Na bit more clearly...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.74,0:14:58.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s coming again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.19,0:14:59.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.61,0:15:01.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.99,0:15:03.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just what is that thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:06.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can you...see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.70,0:15:08.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.28,0:15:10.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.19,0:15:14.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s so clearly visible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.19,0:15:17.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.03,0:15:21.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mister, behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.47,0:15:29.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Gone? Where’d it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:33.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you looking, Mister?!\NTo your right! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:39.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mister, don’t tell me\Nyou can’t see him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.19,0:15:41.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can see just a bit of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:44.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Which means,\Nyou really don’t see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:45.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It can’t be helped then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:48.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hold me tight.\NI’ll see him for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:51.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?! You can’t!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:53.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can! Let me do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.13,0:15:57.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not the first time\NI’ve seen a monster like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.40,0:16:01.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s bothering me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:06.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,what do they have to\Ndo with Ichigo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:08.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:10.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To the left. Dodge!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.07,0:16:24.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.19,0:16:32.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.14,0:16:34.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.45,0:16:35.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.11,0:16:37.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.28,0:16:39.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.11,0:16:41.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:44.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This guy’s covered in blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.03,0:16:46.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did you fight him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:47.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did you beat him up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:51.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid! Don’t come!\NGet away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.66,0:16:53.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What a thing to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.98,0:16:56.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We’re just worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.33,0:16:58.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re always like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:17:02.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.90,0:17:05.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.90,0:17:21.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t tell me you hit\Nsomeone again, Yasutora?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.57,0:17:25.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the point of\Nhitting someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.25,0:17:30.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You hurt those who hurt you,\Nand what’s left?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.61,0:17:38.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yasutora, you are strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.11,0:17:42.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are big.\NYou are beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.74,0:17:48.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You were born with everything\Npeople wish from God.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.19,0:17:51.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,People who are different\Nare suppressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:53.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know about other things,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.42,0:17:57.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but that’s the way things\Nare in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.53,0:17:59.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But Yasutora...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.66,0:18:03.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You must be kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.19,0:18:09.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You must learn why you\Nhave such big, strong fists.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.19,0:18:11.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:16.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know, Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.61,0:18:21.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My fists aren’t big so that\NI can hurt others.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.78,0:18:24.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My body...is big...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.92,0:18:27.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so that I can protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:31.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.45,0:18:33.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.10,0:18:37.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But that’s why...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.32,0:18:38.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,even just a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.86,0:18:42.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to lend me\Nyour strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:07.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What...is that arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.24,0:19:18.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:42.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mister! Your arm...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.19,0:19:44.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.47,0:19:53.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So un-cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.32,0:19:54.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you make a gesture\Nlike that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.36,0:20:00.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.32,0:20:02.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.05,0:20:05.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That armor on my right arm\Nappeared out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.97,0:20:09.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And from it... something\Namazing was released.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.70,0:20:11.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And suddenly, I could see\Nthat monster so clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.64,0:20:16.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t understand...\Nnot at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.20,0:20:18.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:25.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re not hurt,\NIchigo’s sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.65,0:20:29.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid! You’re the only one\Nwho’s hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.49,0:20:33.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That’s good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.53,0:20:35.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:41.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What’s good about getting hurt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.28,0:20:44.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If even one person\Ngets hurt, it’s NOT good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.19,0:20:48.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s just the logic of guys\Nwho want to be all heroic!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.19,0:20:50.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In that sense,\Nyou’re just like Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:53.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Aghh! I can’t stand it!\NYou just wait here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.12,0:20:56.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll call my dad and\Nhave him treat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:20:58.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t move from that spot, Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.49,0:21:04.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo’s sister, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.70,0:21:08.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Ichigo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.32,0:21:12.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the way she kicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.23,0:22:03.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Though the voyage must continue on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.49,0:22:08.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,May seas always be calm
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.65,0:22:13.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When the cycle of the moon\Nhas renewed may it shine
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.71,0:22:18.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's light to guide your boat
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.97,0:22:23.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I offer this voyage a prayer
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.40,0:22:28.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With each new day that still awaits
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.35,0:22:32.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,On vividly shining seas
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.74,0:22:39.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To the end of the journey
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.45,0:22:44.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Into a somber Karakura town\Nunder attack by monsters
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.12,0:22:46.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,suddenly appears\Nthe Fighter of Hope, Orihime!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.51,0:22:51.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With six henchmen,\Nshe tosses out evil one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.14,0:22:52.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.83,0:22:54.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Next week's preview.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.12,0:22:55.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's too convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.28,0:22:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,